
	WordPress Github Repos
	
	Author: Ryan Boswell
			ryanboswell.com
			github.com/ryanboswell/WordPress-GitHub-Repos
	
	Usage:
	
	1) Upload the "wordpress-github-repos" folder to "/wp-content/plugins/".
	2) Activate the plugin in WordPress.
	3) Stick the shortcode into your page: [github_repos username="YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME"]
	4) Enjoy!
	
	
